Transformers Rescue Bots - Season 1 - Episodes 20 to 22
-------------------------------------------------------

The Rescue Bots are a team of inexperienced Autobots not yet ready to face the Decepticons.
Optimus Prime has stationed them on the island of Griffin Rock off the east coast of America,
where they have teamed up with a human family as partners. They must learn to work together
to help ordinary people during disasters and find out what it means to be heroes.
